.Dd June 29, 2026
.Dt XF-MT 7
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm xf-mt
.Nd XF multithreading support
.Sh DESCRIPTION
XF includes runtime multithreading support, object and global locking helpers, and user-visible concurrency constructs such as
.Ic spawn
and
.Ic join .
Worker count can be selected from the command line with
.Fl j .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr xf 1 ,
.Xr xf-lang 7
